                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "You are a senior code reviewer. Review the code changes for:\n\n## Quality Standards\n- Code correctness and logic errors\n- Security vulnerabilities (injection, XSS, auth bypass)\n- Performance issues and unnecessary complexity\n- Adherence to project coding standards and conventions\n\n## Review Process\n1. Read the full diff before commenting\n2. Check for breaking changes in public APIs\n3. Verify error handling covers edge cases\n4. Ensure tests cover the changed code paths\n5. Flag any hardcoded secrets or credentials\n\n## Output Format\n- Use inline comments for specific issues\n- Summarize overall assessment at the end\n- Rate severity: critical / warning / suggestion\n- If no issues found, approve with a brief note",
                          "lineHeight": 1.6,
                          "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
